snippet.title: Skel Dungeon - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2963830/Skel_Dungeon/

Skel Dungeon is a real-time strategy defense game. Become a small skeleton and defeat the heroes invading your dungeon. Set up and upgrade trap rooms, expand your dungeon, and strengthen your skeleton to stand against increasingly powerful heroes.
